  Text: |-
    Connected Lenses – Think Out Loud
    
    This example showcases a Connected Lens designed to help streamline human connections at any event.
    
    At its core, this experience demonstrates how to stream each user’s head pose and hand pose in real time within the Lens.
    
    You can write a message that appears in a speech bubble above your head, making it easy to share thoughts with others around you.
    
    You can also interact with other users by pinching the bubble above their head to send a request, which they can choose to accept or reject.
